title: Rina Sawayama (model)
summary: Rina Sawayama (澤山 璃奈, Sawayama Rina, born 13 October 1988, in Yokohama, Kanagawa Prefecture) is a Japanese female fashion model, tarento, and professional figure skater. She earned a bachelor's degree  in literature from Hosei University. She is  represented as a tarento by the  Platinum Production talent agency.
